#: org.kde.powerplant.metainfo.xml:8
msgid "PowerPlant"
msgstr "पावरप्लांट"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.powerplant.metainfo.xml:9
msgid "Keep your plants alive"
msgstr "भवतः वनस्पतयः जीविताः कुर्वन्तु"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.powerplant.metainfo.xml:17
msgid ""
"PowerPlant lets you track when your plants have to be watered and how their "
"health develops over time."
msgstr ""
"PowerPlant इत्यनेन भवन्तः कदा भवतः वनस्पतयः जलं दातव्याः, कालान्तरे तेषां स्वास्थ्यस्य "
"विकासः कथं भवति इति निरीक्षणं कर्तुं शक्नोति।"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.powerplant.metainfo.xml:31
msgid "Main view with the list of plants."
msgstr "वनस्पतयः सूचीसहितं मुख्यदृश्यम्।"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.powerplant.metainfo.xml:35
msgid "Details of a plant."
msgstr "कस्यचित् पादपस्य विवरणम् ।"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
